    "name": "Forgotten Fears",
    "steam_appid": 3028210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Experience five different levels:</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Forest:</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a forest keeper. Your task is to <strong>bring light to the forest</strong> while avoiding danger lurking in the dark. You have your trusty <strong>flashlight</strong> and <strong>a map</strong> that will guide your way, but be careful, as <strong>the flashlight battery is limited</strong>. <strong>Light all the lamps marked on the map</strong> to provide safety for yourself and the forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/89522d14ae516abd27fcb8311830b187.poster.avif?t=1734696017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/89522d14ae516abd27fcb8311830b187.webm?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/89522d14ae516abd27fcb8311830b187.mp4?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Underwater:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After an accident, you wake up underwater in a small cage and quickly realize, that <strong>you are not alone</strong>. You must <strong>find several items</strong> that will help you. <strong>Explore the cage quietly, so you don't disturb the danger</strong>, and find the items before you run out of oxygen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/f7ff3ad7effc174d28f4e6be877f76b7.poster.avif?t=1734696017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/f7ff3ad7effc174d28f4e6be877f76b7.webm?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/f7ff3ad7effc174d28f4e6be877f76b7.mp4?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Cottage:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a long drive, you have finally arrived at an abandoned cottage with paranormal activity. <strong>Find the way to open the basement door</strong>. <strong>Explore the house, find hidden objects, solve puzzles, unlock blocked areas</strong>, and take what belongs to you. But be careful, as <strong>you are not alone</strong>. You have your flashlight to help you out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/a44a657920e6aaf602e86f5be2ae262b.poster.avif?t=1734696017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/a44a657920e6aaf602e86f5be2ae262b.webm?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/a44a657920e6aaf602e86f5be2ae262b.mp4?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>UNKNOWN:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are in the UNKNOWN place, there is no light, no day, no night, no exit. <strong>Find and pull 10 levers to open the escape from this place</strong>. <strong>Avoid the traps and the danger lurking in the dark</strong>. You can find different monitors in the labyrinth, some of them will show you how much time is left, how many levers you have to pull, and also the minimap to orient yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/6b2c2e5feadba4fb4b217a4745130cf5.poster.avif?t=1734696017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/6b2c2e5feadba4fb4b217a4745130cf5.webm?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/6b2c2e5feadba4fb4b217a4745130cf5.mp4?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Basement:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You've got your first job as an &quot;Anomaly Huntsman&quot;. You arrived at the place and quickly got to work. You have a computer to monitor and report anomalies. The first few hours were quite silent, but as the night progressed anomalies started appearing faster and faster, sometimes even appearing in your room. Use your computer to fix anomalies and environment to stay safe from anomalies that occur in your room.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/4f80df77b7ab9d8420501b2c2d2d5f25.poster.avif?t=1734696017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/4f80df77b7ab9d8420501b2c2d2d5f25.webm?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028210/extras/4f80df77b7ab9d8420501b2c2d2d5f25.mp4?t=1734696017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
